        <img class="exit-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0838/7991/files/x_50.png?49609" /><p class="FAQ-answer">Your membership is automatically added to your cart when you checkout for the first time.</p>
        
        <p class="FAQ-question">My annual membership is almost up. What happens next?</p>
        <img class="exit-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0838/7991/files/x_50.png?49609" /><p class="FAQ-answer">So you can enjoy uninterrupted benefits, your membership will automatically renew and you will be charged your annual membership fee. If you wish to cancel your account you can email our customer service team at <a href="mailto:service@publicgoods.com?Subject=Annual%20membership" class="underline" target="_blank">service@publicgoods.com.</a></p>
        
        <p class="FAQ-question">I’d like to cancel my membership.</p>
        <img class="exit-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0838/7991/files/x_50.png?49609" /><p class="FAQ-answer">We'll miss you but, to cancel your free trial or annual membership account, email our customer service team at <a href="mailto:service@publicgoods.com?Subject=Cancel%20membership" class="underline" target="_blank">service@publicgoods.com.</a> 
		For annual memberships, please note that we refund a prorated membership fee for each month that your annual membership is active. </p>
        
        <p class="FAQ-question">I’m having trouble logging in.</p>
        <img class="exit-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0838/7991/files/x_50.png?49609" /><p class="FAQ-answer">You can reset your password <a href="https://www.publicgoods.com/account/login" class="underline" target="_blank">here </a> by clicking "Forgot your password?" If you need further assistance, please email our customer service team at <a href="mailto:service@publicgoods.com?Subject=Login%20trouble" class="underline" target="_blank">service@publicgoods.com.</a></p>
        
